CONCLUSION
Knowing how individual moovements affect population moovements can improve our understanding of population dynamics. Moovements of individual in populations is important to understand how individuals and different populations get mixed. We should also try to understand how different environmental conditions affect moovement. It might be that the new technologies will allow this. Hower, this was written 10 years ago. I should look for new papers.
